<strong>Eligible countries<\/strong>: international applicants can participate in this award program.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Admissible criteria:<\/strong> for applying for this educational award, seekers must have to complete the following criteria for qualification:<\/li>\n<li>All applicants must have a previous degree for entry in undergraduate study<\/li>\n<li>Candidates have to be enrolled in undergraduate degree coursework<\/li>\n<li>All international students are eligible to apply for bursaries.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"supporting-documents\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Supporting_documents\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80012367\"><\/a>Supporting documents<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Applicants are required to submit the following credentials<\/strong><strong>:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Transcripts<\/li>\n<li>Letter of recommendation<\/li>\n<li>A resume<\/li>\n<li>Photocopy of passport and all the previous necessary mark-sheet.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"acceptable-course-subjects\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Acceptable_Course_Subjects\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80012368\"><\/a>Acceptable Course \/ Subjects<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The award is available for undergraduate degree coursework in any subject area.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-procedure\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Procedure\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80012369\"><\/a>Application Procedure<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><a name=\"_Toc80012370\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80011915\"><\/a><strong>Application Procedure<\/strong><strong> is as follows:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a name=\"_Toc80012371\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80011916\"><\/a>How to apply: to be enlisted in this award program, aspirants are required to take <a href=\"https:\/\/admissions.oregonstate.edu\/international\/prices-scholarships\/scholarships-international-students\/undergraduate-scholarships\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">admission<\/a> in the undergraduate degree course work t the university . after taking confirmation; you will be eligible for the bursary.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Admission Necessities: <\/strong>For taking admission, aspirants need to hold their previous degree certificates<\/p>\n<p><strong>Language Requirements:\u00a0<\/strong>Candidates need to show their English language level by submitting an acceptable certificate of English language aptitude.<\/p>\n<p>To apply click <a href=\"https:\/\/www.scholarshipsads.com\/international-regional-scholarship-awards-at-oregon-state-university\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/p>\n<p>See also&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/cbu-graduate-programs\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CBU Graduate programs\/Cape Breton University Admission<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Orgon State University Scholarship &#8211; Scholarship Description, Eligibility criteria, Supporting Documents, Acceptable Course\/ Subjects, Application Procedures, and benefits.&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1387,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[14],"tags":[779],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1386"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1386"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1386\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":19202,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1386\/revisions\/19202"}],"